data.description: Welcome all Investors! Welcome to this beautiful home located in Apollo Beach, Florida. Open floor concept with granite countertops, 42" wood cabinets, stainless steel appliances and large kitchen island; perfect for entertaining. The home has a split floor plan and the Master Bedroom and En Suite has lots of privacy. Stand up shower in the Master Bath, granite countertops along with a separate private water closet. The Master Bedroom has two separate closets. The 2 secondary Bedrooms have ample space. Osprey Landing has a low HOA and no CDD and is a gated community. Conveniently located near shopping, restaurants, highways and beaches. Investors welcome. Minor TLC needed; needs new flooring, paint and lawncare maintenance.
